      </div>

      <div type="history" n="locations"><head>Locations</head><p>Found: <rs type="found"><rs type="monuList" key="HadrBath">Hadrianic Baths</rs>: dump of stones west of the baths.</rs>. Original location: <rs type="origLocation">An unidentified church: crowning the chancel barrier.</rs>. Last recorded location: <rs type="lastLocation">Museum.</rs>. </p></div>

      

      

